						<div class="postbody">I'm just wondering if there is any documentation on rewriting games for the Nintendo Entertainment System to the Game Boy Color. I got time and I fan game I want to work on that I would like the better hardware of the Game Boy Color to work with, but I would like to keep a similar game play to the original; I just wanted to make a sort of fan sequel with some additional features. Also on a side note I know that some Game Boy Color games were backwards compatible with the original game boy, is there any documentation on that?</div>

